{"tid":1638173,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"新技能解鎖？？勇武戰術討論mon post狗勿入","createTime":"2019-10-08T08:31:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-09T05:24:25.000Z","uid":206787,"like":14,"dislike":52,"uniUserReply":64,"replies":[{"pid":"f50a18c1c2581d891c70b3776af5a205bbfbacf2","tid":1638173,"uid":206787,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T08:31:39.000Z","msg":"經過四個月，傘陣我相信大家都唔陌生，但大家有無諗過一個比傘陣更好用嘅盾？？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n以下係小弟突發奇想嘅諗法：<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n就係360度完美防禦波波球<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yiTbr9U.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyiTbr9U.jpg&h=c2ccb86f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n如果用呢個做盾上前線 佢圓型充氣嘅設計 應該可以充分卸開 海綿彈 同布袋彈嘅力<br />\n<br />\n同時你又可以繼續推進<br />\n<br />\n加上個波體積大 後面嘅手足 又可以哩埋係個後面一齊推 <br />\n<br />\n魔法師 又可以有掩體 放魔法<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n如果你話走個陣唔方便<br />\n<br />\n你又可以縮起隻腳，變成個波碌走，班狗成身gear咁重， 一定跑唔嬴你。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/m5gwr9R.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fm5gwr9R.jpg&h=983100f6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n再唔係打近戰，又可以一野撞9開佢，佢支警棍又打你唔入。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/u5AX69S.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fu5AX69S.jpg&h=744980e1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n如果成班前線 ,一人一個 一齊推進,我相信咩狗都要收皮。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DCapM9T.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDCapM9T.jpg&h=78834466&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n同埋佢攜帶方便，走同去個程放氣，之後再即場充氣，就算你去個陣被狗搜身嗰陣都鋤你唔入。可以話係居家旅行，發夢必備。<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">光復香港 時代革命</span></span>"},{"pid":"d9320601e82696bf20d9ceb5def9f66b01d26d2e","tid":1638173,"uid":206787,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T08:32:05.000Z","msg":"自推（1/10）"},{"pid":"1726c69773a236401429b5892bf1a12c03d0c333","tid":1638173,"uid":216992,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T08:32:29.000Z","msg":"cls<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac594872a23da00a36359773c5ad20c588ac8aa9","tid":1638173,"uid":11254,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T08:32:29.000Z","msg":"ON9 你行到再講"},{"pid":"2057ccfccb54479f186f71220b00bc726129a98b","tid":1638173,"uid":302,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T08:32:49.000Z","msg":"沒有更弱智<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔割唔割<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93c5b2f0305fb718298fe191b8de