\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/m5gwr9R.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fm5gwr9R.jpg&h=983100f6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n再唔係打近戰，又可以一野撞9開佢，佢支警棍又打你唔入。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/u5AX69S.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fu5AX69S.jpg&h=744980e1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n如果成班前線 ,一人一個 一齊推進,我相信咩狗都要收皮。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DCapM9T.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDCapM9T.jpg&h=78834466&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n同埋佢攜帶方便，走同去個程放氣，之後再即場充氣，就算你去個陣被狗搜身嗰陣都鋤你唔入。可以話係居家旅行，發夢必備。<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">光復香港 時代革命</span></span>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T08:39:19.000Z","msg":"黐線點支煙已經攪撚掂你邊度都唔駛去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9bafd2a1ae08b48f53333682ca4ae2750d7c073f","tid":1638173,"uid":308674,"like":0,"d